Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.12,0:00:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Hadorra!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.00,0:00:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.51,0:00:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The Hero defeated the Dark Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.43,0:00:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no telling\Nwhat humans are capable of.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.78,0:00:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Just who do you think you are?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.39,0:01:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Begone! Begone, humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.37,0:03:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,DAI, THE TINY HERO
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.36,0:03:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai, the Hero is here!\NYippee! Go, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.05,0:03:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Defend the island's peace!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.75,0:03:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You imbecile!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.33,0:03:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.69,0:03:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that for, Grampa Burasu?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.29,0:04:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have time to play Hero,\Nthen do your magic training!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.23,0:04:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Aww...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.80,0:04:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,How many years has it been\Nsince I found you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.95,0:04:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of Hero\Ncan't even learn a single spell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.94,0:04:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so annoying, Gomechan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.65,0:04:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Grampa Burasu is the one\Nwho told me about the Hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.99,0:04:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,There once was a swordman of justice,\Ncalled the Hero,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.09,0:04:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,who fought the Dark Lord,\Na tormentor of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.60,0:04:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Hero, together with his companions,\Ndefeated the Dark Lord at last!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.00,0:04:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.50,0:04:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We monsters, who were\Nunder the thrall of the Dark Lord,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.82,0:04:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,were freed from his evil will\Nand came to live here on Dermline Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.51,0:04:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all thanks to the Hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.49,0:04:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The Hero sounds amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.64,0:04:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai, you're to become a brilliant Mage,\Nso that you can help the Hero someday!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.69,0:05:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Grampa just says that\Nbecause he's a Mage...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.65,0:05:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,but I wanna be a Hero.\NIt sounds the coolest.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.70,0:05:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You agree don't you, Gomechan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.50,0:05:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew you'd get me, Gomechan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.09,0:05:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.42,0:05:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.72,0:05:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.55,0:05:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.72,0:05:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a Hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.27,0:05:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Why's a Hero coming to this island?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.74,0:05:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't just sit here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.15,0:05:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait here, Gomechan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.69,0:05:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hup!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.24,0:05:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Merman, take me to that boat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.37,0:05:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I might just meet a real Hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.33,0:06:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,For an island supposedly\Ninfested by monsters, it seems peaceful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.69,0:06:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since the Dark Lord died,\Nthey've all gone docile.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.47,0:06:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,All we do is knock them around\Nand people worship us as Heroes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.74,0:06:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk about an easy business.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.72,0:06:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed. I can't wait to cut loose again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.31,0:06:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't just slaughter them. It's not\Nan extermination mission this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.13,0:06:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The one-of-a-kind mythical creature,\Nthe Golden Metal Slime.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.32,0:06:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it really exist?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.59,0:06:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.57,0:06:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,A Merman!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.78,0:06:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a child riding it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.87,0:06:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! It's really you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.26,0:06:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a Hero, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.10,0:06:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.\NThe Hero and his noble companions.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.81,0:07:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.10,0:07:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Little boy, who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.31,0:07:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.44,0:07:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You're from that island?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.63,0:07:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.32,0:07:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But isn't that island full of monsters?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.92,0:07:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine. They're all my friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.78,0:07:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.37,0:07:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,They're your friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.12,0:07:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You want me to call everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.06,0:07:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.02,0:07:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We go around protecting innocent monsters\Nso they aren't bullied by humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.11,0:07:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So we want to know\Nthe monsters' situation on this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.43,0:07:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it for us, Dai.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.56,0:07:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.90,0:07:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The assembly whistle? What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.71,0:08:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Little boy, is this all of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.82,0:08:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep. Almost.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.48,0:08:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, isn't there one like this,\Nbut more pretty?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.24,0:08:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.57,0:08:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! You mean Gomechan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.06,0:08:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Gomechan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.31,0:08:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a nickname! The entire name is\NGolden whatchamacallit,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.08,0:08:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,but that's too difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.27,0:08:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.65,0:08:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.29,0:08:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd really love to meet Gomechan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.65,0:08:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a little shy, so I'll go get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.70,0:08:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, everyone? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.71,0:08:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, there's a surviving Lump Shaman.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.58,0:08:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.23,0:08:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Deroline the Hero and his companions.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.01,0:08:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,A Hero?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.43,0:08:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I sense something malicious about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.89,0:09:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you come here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.47,0:09:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What an obnoxious geezer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.48,0:09:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you struggling?! It's a Hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.86,0:09:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.20,0:09:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Hyado!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.37,0:09:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,S...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.46,0:09:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.67,0:09:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai, run!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.59,0:09:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Grampa!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.97,0:09:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, little boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.14,0:09:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's a reward for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.15,0:09:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Bagi!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.53,0:09:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.53,0:10:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's clean up and get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.16,0:10:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone get down!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.83,0:10:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}IO!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.01,0:10:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Those scoundrels!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.97,0:10:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That went well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.72,0:10:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have whatever we want now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.43,0:10:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't stop laughing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.73,0:10:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would a Hero do this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.58,0:10:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would a Hero kidnap Gomechan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.21,0:10:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That Hero was a fake!\NNo Hero would do something like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.09,0:10:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Grampa!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.24,0:10:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to go save Gomechan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.78,0:10:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to fight them, use these.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.71,0:10:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What are these?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.54,0:10:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Magic Cylinders.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.75,0:10:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can't use magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.19,0:10:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. Each Cylinder\Ncan trap one living creature within.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.63,0:11:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Just say "Derupa," and they'll suck in\Nwhoever you point a Cylinder at.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.99,0:11:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Say "Iruru" to release the contents.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.70,0:11:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.39,0:11:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Come up with a plan\Nand attack with your friends. Also...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.42,0:11:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,these Gold Cylinders were given to me\Nby the Dark Lord long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.36,0:11:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I was too scared\Nto find out what they contain.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.46,0:11:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,-Derupa?\N-Just in case...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.12,0:11:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Iruru!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.58,0:11:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,-Imbecile! Why...\N-{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Derupa!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.66,0:11:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Iruru!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.75,0:11:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,-...are you...\N-{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Derupa!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.88,0:11:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.67,0:11:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! That's Grampa for starters!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.42,0:11:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And now...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.84,0:11:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone who can still fight, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.44,0:11:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.15,0:12:00.61,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}IRURU{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}/{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}DERUPA{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.16,0:12:05.62,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}MERA{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}\NFIRE-TYPE SPELL
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.28,0:12:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Deroline, the Hero. Raise your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.41,0:12:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Majesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.79,0:12:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So, how was Dermline Island?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.02,0:12:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it a dark hive of monsters\Nas rumors say?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.34,0:12:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Evil remnant monsters assaulted us\Nin an endless stream,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.84,0:12:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,but, together with my companions,\Nwe vanquished them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.56,0:12:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,-Wow!\N-Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.45,0:12:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,A true Hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.83,0:12:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,During this, we captured a rare monster\Nof which only one exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.19,0:12:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We offer it to you, King Romos.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.36,0:12:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,A monster for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.16,0:12:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-This is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.91,0:12:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Called the mythical creature,\Nit is the Golden Metal Slime.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.22,0:12:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Truly a living jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.25,0:12:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,How magnificent!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.27,0:13:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done, Deroline!\NYou may have the reward you requested!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.55,0:13:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The Romos family symbol of a Hero,\Nthe Crown of Champions!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.64,0:13:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You are truly a Hero worthy of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.27,0:13:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,-What's that?\N-It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.69,0:13:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Give back Gomechan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.07,0:13:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Gomechan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.30,0:13:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That Golden whatchamacallit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.58,0:13:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Get back, King Romos.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.31,0:13:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,He may look innocent,\Nbut he's with those vicious monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.23,0:13:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,My friends aren't vicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.61,0:13:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But they can be against people like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.80,0:13:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do this, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.39,0:13:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Iruru!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.77,0:13:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Iruru!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.86,0:14:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Iruru!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.27,0:14:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Iruru!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.86,0:14:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,...sucking me in?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.20,0:14:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't take a hint! You'll regret this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.16,0:14:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, hang on!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.00,0:14:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you like that?!\NAttacks from air, land, and sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.43,0:14:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll get you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.39,0:14:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Mera!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.61,0:14:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay away!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.83,0:15:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Masopho, let's put them on ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.88,0:15:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,-{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Bagi!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}\N-{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Hyado!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.30,0:15:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Now! Let's get those monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.93,0:15:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.35,0:15:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Mera!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.27,0:15:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Mera!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.98,0:15:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Hyado!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.53,0:15:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}IO!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.75,0:15:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Stupid monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.22,0:15:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Why you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.58,0:15:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't underestimate a Hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.94,0:15:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You're no Hero!\NYou're a crook who kidnapped my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.59,0:15:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.55,0:15:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.35,0:15:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.35,0:15:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm your opponent here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.31,0:16:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll silence you for good!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.40,0:16:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The Golden Cylinders!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.11,0:16:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Use the Golden Cylinders, Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.78,0:16:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.95,0:16:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Iruru!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.50,0:16:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Not one, but several?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.92,0:16:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You startled me! They're just Slimes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.71,0:16:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Iruru!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.39,0:16:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,A d-d-d-...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.89,0:16:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,A Dragon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.48,0:16:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Bagi!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.44,0:16:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Good going, Dragon! Get that fake Hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.00,0:17:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.92,0:17:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, little boy.\NGet that Dragon to back off.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.97,0:17:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Gomechan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.80,0:17:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.01,0:17:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.07,0:17:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Derupa!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.23,0:17:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice going, Zulbon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.11,0:17:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.07,0:17:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like we win.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.37,0:17:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,These were all...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.58,0:17:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,A King Slime?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.75,0:17:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Zulbon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.26,0:17:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So a King Slime came out in pieces!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.72,0:17:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay away!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.35,0:18:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.93,0:18:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Derupa!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.15,0:18:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You did it, Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.20,0:18:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Gomechan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.20,0:18:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.51,0:18:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.37,0:18:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.29,0:18:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,They said they\Nwere a Hero and his companions,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.43,0:18:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,but no Hero would try to kill a child\Nor take hostages!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.59,0:18:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The King of Romos?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.59,0:18:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Get back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.69,0:18:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough. Let us hear out this monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.72,0:18:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.85,0:18:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems as though my eyes were clouded.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.23,0:18:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,How could I let them go to Dermline Island\Nwithout realizing they were fakes?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.78,0:19:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai's acts of violence were out of\Nhis wish to save his friend. Have mercy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.41,0:19:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir Burasu, it is I who should\Nbeg for forgiveness.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.10,0:19:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring it forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.09,0:19:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps this brave child is the one truly\Nworthy of wearing this Crown of Champions.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.55,0:19:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I bestow this to the future Hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.60,0:19:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The future Hero...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.82,0:19:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, let us continue on our way\Nto the Papnica Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.36,0:19:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! Don't leave us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.05,0:19:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.87,0:19:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's my Crown of Champions?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.37,0:19:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm? Don't ask me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.00,0:19:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my treasure!\NWhere did you hide it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.76,0:20:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.32,0:20:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, you have no use for\Nsomething for a Hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.30,0:20:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the future Hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.99,0:20:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Your future is as a Mage!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.93,0:20:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And nothing else!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.56,0:20:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh come on, Grampa!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.30,0:20:21.03,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,THREE MONTHS LATER
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.66,0:20:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Mera!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.04,0:20:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Pathetic!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.97,0:20:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.50,0:20:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Grampa, I wanna do Hero training!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.19,0:20:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need such training!\NLet's continue!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.40,0:20:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Aww...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.57,0:20:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? It's a ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.34,0:20:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.01,0:20:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! It's a battleship!\NA battleship is invading!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.91,0:20:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.93,0:20:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that a battleship?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.81,0:21:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the Sacred Ship. A special ship\Nthat only a Sage is allowed to use.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.13,0:21:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.49,0:21:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that a Sage?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.37,0:21:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Get your head down!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.02,0:21:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.71,0:21:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You are Dai, the Future Hero\Nand Burasu, the Venerable?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.21,0:21:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The Future Hero?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.53,0:21:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,B-Burasu, the Venerable?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.63,0:21:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Bishop Temjin of Papnica Kingdom,\Nand this is Varon, the Sage.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.53,0:21:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We have come to this island with\NPrincess Leona of Papnica on a mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.14,0:21:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The Princess?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.66,0:21:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.49,0:21:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you Dai, the Hero?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.03,0:21:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.79,0:21:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh wow, you're so tiny!\NTalk about undependable!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.85,0:23:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Princess Leona of Papnica Kingdom\Narrives at Dermline Island.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.18,0:23:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dai guides her across the island,\Nbut mysterious monsters attack.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.36,0:23:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dai and Leona fall into peril.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.19,0:23:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just then,\NDai is enveloped in a mysterious light!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.95,0:23:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Next time on{\i0}\NDRAGON QUEST The Adventure of Dai{\i1},{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.18,0:23:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Dai and Princess Leona"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.05,0:23:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The adventure continues!{\i0}
